"title": "5733: pregnancy",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5733",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<h2>Pregnancy regarded as a blessing from God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:1\">GEN 4:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:17\">GEN 4:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen16:4\">GEN 16:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen20:17-Gen20:18\">GEN 20:17–20:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen29:32\">GEN 29:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen30:1-Gen30:2\">GEN 30:1–30:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen30:4-Gen30:6\">GEN 30:4–30:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen30:17\">GEN 30:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen30:23\">GEN 30:23</a></p>\n<h2>Pregnancy after barrenness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen25:21\">GEN 25:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen30:22-Gen30:23\">GEN 30:22–30:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:1-1Sam1:20\">1SA 1:1–1:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:11-2Kgs4:17\">2KI 4:11–4:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:24-Luke1:25\">LUK 1:24–1:25</a></p>\n<h2>Pregnancy in old age</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:36-Luke1:37\">LUK 1:36–1:37</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:9-Gen18:15\">GEN 18:9–18:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen21:1-Gen21:7\">GEN 21:1–21:7</a></p>\n<h2>Ritual uncleanness after pregnancy</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev12:1-Lev12:7\">LEV 12:1–12:7</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Pregnancy outside marriage</h2>\n<h3>As a result of incest</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen19:30-Gen19:38\">GEN 19:30–19:38</a></strong></p>\n<h3>As a result of prostitution</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen38:24-Gen38:25\">GEN 38:24–38:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen38:13-Gen38:19\">GEN 38:13–38:19</a></p>\n<h3>As a result of adultery</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam11:2-2Sam11:5\">2SA 11:2–11:5</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Pregnancy in troubled times sometimes a misfortune</h2>\n<h3>Because of atrocities committed in war</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs15:16\">2KI 15:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs8:12\">2KI 8:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos13:16\">HOS 13:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos1:13\">AMO 1:13</a></p>\n<h3>Because of additional hardship in harsh circumstances</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:15-Matt24:21\">MAT 24:15–24:21</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:14-Mark13:19\">MRK 13:14–13:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:20-Luke21:24\">LUK 21:20–21:24</a></p>\n<h2>Premature birth</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod21:22-Exod21:25\">EXO 21:22–21:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam4:19\">1SA 4:19</a></p>\n<h2>Labour pains</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:3\">1TH 5:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:16\">GEN 3:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam4:19\">1SA 4:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev12:2\">REV 12:2</a></p>\n<h2>Miscarriage</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:25-Exod23:26\">EXO 23:25–23:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen31:38\">GEN 31:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job21:10\">JOB 21:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos9:14\">HOS 9:14</a></p>\n<h2>Figurative use of pregnancy</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps7:14\">PSA 7:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos9:11\">HOS 9:11</a></p>",
